272\">{{cite web |last=Lee |first=Amy |title=Change of heart |url=http://www.evthreads.com/showpost.php?p=136272&postcount=204 |work=EvThreads.com |accessdate=June 28, 2013 |authorlink=Amy Lee |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120206010232/http://www.evthreads.com/showpost.php?p=136272&postcount=204 |archivedate=February 6, 2012 |date=January 29, 2007}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"lafm25563\">{{cite news |title=Escuche: \u2018Weight of the world\u2019 lo nuevo de Evanescence |url=http://www.lafm.com.co/noticia.php3?nt=25563 |work=[[La FM]] |accessdate=September 12, 2013 |archiveurl=https://archive.today/20120629170213/http://www.lafm.com.co/noticia.php3?nt=25563 |archivedate=June 29, 2012 |language=Spanish}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"vh1songs\">{{cite web |url=http://www.vh1.com/news/articles/1540914/story.jhtml |title=Evanescence: Amy Lee Explains the New Songs |first=C. |last=Bottomley |publisher=[[VH1]]. [[Viacom (2005\u2013present)|Viacom]] |date=October 8, 2006 |accessdate=March 25, 2007 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120423193504/http://www.vh1.com/news/articles/1540914/story.jhtml |archivedate=April 23, 2012}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"fillingbenshoes\">{{cite web |title=Evanescence Guitarist: Filling Ben Moody's Shoes |url=http://www.ultimate-guitar.com/interviews/interviews/evanescence_guitarist_filling_ben_moodys_shoes.html |work=[[Ultimate Guitar]] |accessdate=July 27, 2013 |date=November 3, 2006 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131231001211/http://www.ultimate-guitar.com/interviews/interviews/evanescence_guitarist_filling_ben_moodys_shoes.html |archivedate=December 31, 2013 }}</ref>\n<ref name=\"unf2010\">{{cite press release |url=http://www.unfoundation.org/news-and-media/press-releases/2010/evanescence-teams-up-with-united-nations-foundation.html |title=Evanescence Teams Up With the United Nations Foundation to Raise Money for Victims of the Earthquake in Haiti |publisher=[[United Nations Foundation]] |date=Januar